<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 de qiú yīn nǐ xuán zhuǎn jiāng hé yīn nǐ liú tǎng
 dà de yīn nǐ xiào lì wàn wù yīn nǐ shēng zhǎng
 tài yáng yīn nǐ fā guāng niǎo ér yīn nǐ fēi xiáng
 tiān kōng yīn nǐ bù zhì yuè ér jiǎo jié xīng ér shǎn liàng
 qīng cǎo yīn nǐ bì lǜ huā ér yīn nǐ piāo xiāng
 wǒ men yīn nǐ fàng shēng gē chàng yīn nǐ huó zhe yǒu xī wàng
 ó yé sū wǒ men yǒu nǐ xīn duō huān chàng
 yīn nǐ dì xiōng huān jù yī táng yīn nǐ yǒu yī gè fāng xiàng
 wǒ men yào wèi nǐ chuán yáng wǒ men yào xìng qǐ fā guāng
 yīn nǐ shì jiè cái yǒu hé píng rén lèi cái yǒu xī wàng</lyrics>
